{"success":true,"message":"操作成功","code":200,"subCode":"","result":{"id":"183","name":"五级地址解析","path":null,"personDayQuato":null,"enterpriseDayQuato":null,"personMinQuato":null,"enterpriseMinQuato":null,"personMonthQuato":null,"enterpriseMonthQuato":null,"personSumQuato":null,"enterpriseSumQuato":null,"code":null,"certificationNeeded":null,"description":null,"owner":null,"firstType":0,"serviceType":1,"secondType":null,"status":2,"requestType":0,"special":0,"applicationType":0,"innerUrl":null,"outerUrl":null,"wordContext":"# 五级地址解析\r\n\r\n## 接口说明\r\n\r\n用户可通过该功能，获取地址的五级行政区划（省、市、区、街道、社区）及相关行政区划代码和城乡分类代码。地址结构越完整，地址内容越准确，解析的准确率越高。\r\n\r\n## API服务地址\r\n``````\r\n生产环境：https://gis-apis.sf-express.com/opquery/addressResolve\r\n请求方式：post/get\r\n``````\r\n\r\n\r\n## 请求参数\r\n<table>\r\n        <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <th>参数名</th>\r\n                <th>类型</th>\r\n                <th>必需</th>\r\n                <th>描述</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n        </thead>\r\n        <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>address</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>是</td>\r\n                <td>输入文本地址，如“广东省深圳市南山区高新南九道麦当劳”，不建议只输入“麦当劳”或者“高新南九道麦当劳”，可能存在同名地方，至少给定一个范围才能确保可识别及识别正确（字段长度限制，1000）</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>province</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>否</td>\r\n                <td>中文省份名称，如“广东省”</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>city</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>否</td>\r\n                <td>中文城市名称，如“深圳市”</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>county</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>否</td>\r\n                <td>中文区县名称，如“南山区”</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>town</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>否</td>\r\n                <td>中文乡镇街道名称，如“粤海街道”</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>ak</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>是</td>\r\n                <td>用户申请的授权码（放header中）</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n    </table>\r\n\r\n### 请求示例\r\n``````json\r\n{\r\n    \"address\":\"河南省三门峡市卢氏县杜关镇郭家村村委会\"\r\n}\r\n``````\r\n\r\n## 返回结果\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n        <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <th>参数名</th>\r\n                <th>类型</th>\r\n                <th>描述</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n        </thead>\r\n        <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>status</td>\r\n                <td>number</td>\r\n                <td>状态码：0-解析成功有结果，1-解析失败</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>result</td>\r\n                <td>object</td>\r\n                <td>结果数据集</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>    query</td>\r\n                <td>object</td>\r\n                <td>查询参数集</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        address</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>请求查询的地址（拼接后的）</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>    data</td>\r\n                <td>object</td>\r\n                <td>响应数据集</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        province</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>服务识别的省份</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        city</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>服务识别的市</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        county</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>服务识别的区(县)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        town</td>\r\n                <td>string</td>\r\n                <td>服务识别的镇（街道）</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td>        vilName</td>\r\n         